{
  "title": "Working with Remotes",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h3><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Setup remote repository</span></h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div>(assuming it doesn't exist already on the remote)</div><div><code style=\"font-size: 11.699999809265137px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392);\">git&nbsp;remote&nbsp;add&nbsp;origin&nbsp;https://github.com/&lt;user&lt;/&lt;repo&gt;.git</code></div><div><br></div><div><code style=\"font-size: 11.699999809265137px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392);\">git&nbsp;push&nbsp;--set-upstream&nbsp;origin&nbsp;master</code></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h3><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Push to remote directory</span></h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><code style=\"font-size: 11.699999809265137px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392);\">git push</code></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h3><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Pull from remote</span></h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><code style=\"font-size: 11.699999809265137px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392);\">git pull</code></div><div><i>equals to get fetch &amp;&amp; git merge</i></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h3><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Fetch</span></h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<span style=\"font-family: Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, Monaco, source-code-pro, monospace; font-size: 11.699999809265137px;\">git fetch&nbsp;</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h3><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Branch</span></h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><code style=\"font-size: 11.699999809265137px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392);\">git branch</code></div><div><br></div><div><code style=\"font-size: 11.699999809265137px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392);\">git branch -a</code><br></div><div>List all available branches (local AND remote branches).</div><div><br></div><div><code style=\"font-size: 11.699999809265137px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392);\">git branch -r</code><br></div><div>or</div><div><code style=\"font-size: 11.699999809265137px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0980392);\">git ls-remote --heads &lt;remote-name&gt;</code><br></div><div>List all remote branches.</div>"
    },
